<li role="presentation"><a href='https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nlmcatalog?term="J%20Shoulder%20Elbow%20Surg"[Title%20Abbreviation]' class="usa-link" role="menuitem">View in NLM Catalog</a></li>
